> I've heard of a program called 'cbw' (crypt breaker's workbench) which can be
> used to do ciphertext-only attacks on files encrypted with crypt. Can anybody
> mail me?

anonymous ftp to ftp.funet.fi  (== nic.funet.fi)
cd to /pub/crypt
use binary transfer to get cbw.tar.z

(use whatever tools are appropriate to your system to reverse compress
and tar).

Hope this helps,
